from the Lille meeting explores aspects of Early Palaeozoic climate evolution, sea-level changes and ocean water chemistry (Munnecke et al., in press Munnecke, A., Calner, M., Harper, D.A.T., (Eds.), in press. Special Issue on Early Palaeozoic sea level and climate. Palaeogeography, Palaeoclimatology, Palaeoecology, 210.Munnecke et al., in press).},
