 question of the role of the paleogeographic setting in the Marinoan snowball event (∼635 Ma) is still an open question, since no reliable Marinoan paleogeographic reconstruction exists due to the paucity of paleomagnetic data. {\textcopyright} 2006 Acad{\'{e}}mie des sciences.},
